Leader is back!

46
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,730
Leader is back!

47
00:03:31,730 --> 00:03:32,810
Charge!

48
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:37,450
Hyah!

49
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:44,930
Pull back now.

50
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:47,290
Shen Tianshu.

51
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:49,060
We’ve got into their base.

52
