Why will we pull back?

53
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:51,650
Shen Tianshu!

54
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:53,290
Li Jinrong and her elite disciples

55
00:03:53,290 --> 00:03:54,530
are coming back.

56
00:03:54,530 --> 00:03:56,650
Once Anping Army arrives,

57
00:03:56,650 --> 00:03:58,370
