Sheng.

62
00:05:02,170 --> 00:05:03,900
Answer me, Sheng!

63
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:08,060
Sheng!

64
00:05:50,290 --> 00:05:51,220
You beast!

65
00:05:51,220 --> 00:05:52,620
How dare you come again!

66
00:06:38,010 --> 00:06:39,780
-Madam.
-Madam.

67
00:06:43,170 --> 00:06:44,900
-Pull back!
-Pull back!

68
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:48,850
Don’t chase them.

69
00:06:51,060 --> 00:06:52,010
Madam.

70
00:06:55,250 --> 00:06:56,780
Li Sheng is down there!

71
00:06:59,170 --> 00:07:00,540
Here he is!

72
00:07:08,010 --> 00:07:09,220
Be careful.

73
00:07:10,100 --> 00:07:10,780
Pull.

74
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:11,730
Pull.

75
00:07:19,410 --> 00:07:20,380
Sheng.

76
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:22,250
Are you all right?

77
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:23,850
Aunt.

78
00:07:23,850 --> 00:07:25,570
You’re finally back.

79
00:07:26,780 --> 00:07:28,250
The Fortress.

80
00:07:28,620 --> 00:07:29,780
Are the enemies repelled?

81
00:07:30,540 --> 00:07:31,660
Yes.

82
00:07:39,010 --> 00:07:40,850
I’ll take some sleep.

83
00:07:46,380 --> 00:07:47,500
Go ahead.

84
00:07:55,620 --> 00:07:57,620
Take good care of Sheng.

85
00:07:57,620 --> 00:07:59,820
I’m going to find things out.

86
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:41,050
My father always said

87
00:08:41,610 --> 00:08:44,400
this blade was a legacy.

88
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:47,740
It means to be.

89
00:08:57,050 --> 00:08:58,300
Mother.

90
00:08:58,300 --> 00:08:59,780
Don’t move.

91
00:09:09,220 --> 00:09:10,930
You injured internally.

92
00:09:10,930 --> 00:09:12,690
You’ll be fine soon.

93
00:09:14,180 --> 00:09:16,930
Certainly Ma Jili won’t hit you hard.

94
00:09:24,130 --> 00:09:25,570
What happened with your inner power?

95
00:09:26,610 --> 00:09:28,740
Who did you meet before?

96
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:31,100
I... A long story.

97
00:09:31,980 --> 00:09:34,250
I met Duan Jiuniang at Huarong.

98
00:09:34,250 --> 00:09:37,100
She transfused Yellow and Green Spirit
into my system,

99
00:09:37,100 --> 00:09:40,420
and told me about her past with Grandpa.

100
00:09:41,250 --> 00:09:43,390
She is a true master.

101
00:09:44,490 --> 00:09:46,900
You were lucky to meet her.

102
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:49,610
Mother.

103
00:09:50,010 --> 00:09:50,900
Li Sheng...

104
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:51,780
He’s fine.

105
00:09:53,610 --> 00:09:55,040
Chuchu found him

106
00:09:55,610 --> 00:09:57,280
hanging under the Feihong Bridge.

107
00:09:59,450 --> 00:10:02,250
Just mind your own business.

108
00:10:03,810 --> 00:10:05,010
Mother.

109
00:10:07,780 --> 00:10:10,340
Where is Xie who came back with me?

110
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:14,220
Do you know who he is?

111
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:15,690
I do.

112
00:10:16,610 --> 00:10:18,570
He travels around in the world,

113
00:10:18,570 --> 00:10:20,860
and makes a living by selling songs.

114
00:10:20,860 --> 00:10:23,180
With two mustaches,

115
00:10:23,180 --> 00:10:25,130
he’s nicknamed Qian Suiyou.

116
00:10:27,450 --> 00:10:28,900
Back then

117
00:10:28,900 --> 00:10:30,690
he trespassed Ximo River

118
00:10:30,690 --> 00:10:32,150
and was supposed to be punished,

119
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:36,020
but he was ordered to do so.

120
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:38,050
-Thanks to him, we could...
-Save it.

121
00:10:38,050 --> 00:10:39,810
Leave his matters aside.

122
00:10:42,980 --> 00:10:44,250
Take a good rest

123
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:45,740
and get recovered first.

124
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,980
Then explain to me

125
00:10:46,980 --> 00:10:49,220
what you have done during your travel.

126
00:11:22,930 --> 00:11:24,310
Time is running out.

127
00:11:55,180 --> 00:11:57,010
Aren’t you dead?

128
00:11:57,010 --> 00:11:58,370
I am not that easy...

129
00:11:58,370 --> 00:12:00,130
to get killed.

130
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:12,130
You...

131
00:12:15,010 --> 00:12:17,130
Nice blade.

132
00:12:17,130 --> 00:12:18,660
Do you like it?

133
00:12:20,540 --> 00:12:22,080
But you can’t take it.

134
00:12:22,860 --> 00:12:24,810
I mean,

135
00:12:24,810 --> 00:12:27,490
you are more talented
and have better understanding

136
00:12:27,490 --> 00:12:28,860
in martial arts.

137
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:33,130
Over so many years,

138
00:12:33,130 --> 00:12:34,980
I’ve been trying to catch up with you,

139
00:12:34,980 --> 00:12:37,540
but I can’t.

140
00:12:37,540 --> 00:12:39,570
I’m reluctant to fall behind.

141
00:12:45,860 --> 00:12:47,570
Don’t gloat.

142
00:12:50,250 --> 00:12:52,050
Listen to me.

143
00:12:52,050 --> 00:12:53,740
The saying has that

144
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:54,660
he who laughs last,

145
00:12:54,660 --> 00:12:57,010
laughs best.

146
00:12:57,010 --> 00:12:58,780
You’re better than me now,

147
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:01,660
but soon I’ll surpass you.

148
00:13:04,370 --> 00:13:05,690
Alright.

149
00:13:05,690 --> 00:13:06,930
Wait and see.

150
00:13:12,490 --> 00:13:14,930
Have... Have some tea.

151
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:41,610
It’s hot.

152
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:50,050
Thank you, Brother.

153
00:14:00,050 --> 00:14:01,660
Who was talking with me?

154
00:14:02,300 --> 00:14:04,490
I didn’t hear it clearly.

155
00:14:08,370 --> 00:14:09,610
Brother.

156
00:14:14,130 --> 00:14:15,370
Take a good rest.

157
00:14:18,570 --> 00:14:20,570
I’ve got goose bumps.

158
00:15:07,340 --> 00:15:10,450
What is Cloud-impelling Palm?

159
00:15:10,450 --> 00:15:13,010
He is so powerful.

160
00:15:13,010 --> 00:15:15,780
But why did he follow me
all the way here?

161
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:40,130
What is the tune?

162
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:43,250
Depart in Departure Sorrow Pavilion.

163
00:15:45,450 --> 00:15:47,370
You’ve heard it a lot along the way.

164
00:15:47,370 --> 00:15:48,810
Why asking again?

165
00:15:55,690 --> 00:15:57,250
I come to see you.

166
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:58,660
Can I come into

167
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,180
your room?

168
00:16:00,180 --> 00:16:01,540
You can’t.

169
00:16:04,180 --> 00:16:06,340
Something is wrong with my ears.

170
00:16:06,340 --> 00:16:08,250
I can’t hear some words clearly.

171
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,860
Since you say I can,

172
00:16:12,860 --> 00:16:14,740
I’ll come in.

173
00:16:14,740 --> 00:16:16,930
Thanks. Come on.

174
00:16:16,930 --> 00:16:18,100
Come on in. Be seated.

175
00:16:19,050 --> 00:16:20,220
We are not strangers.

176
00:16:20,220 --> 00:16:21,810
No need to receive me outside.

177
00:16:21,810 --> 00:16:22,860
Sit.

178
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:34,220
Miss.

179
00:16:34,220 --> 00:16:36,340
Why are you staring at me like that?

180
00:16:38,490 --> 00:16:40,930
I’m handsome.

181
00:16:40,930 --> 00:16:42,250
You should pay money

182
00:16:42,250 --> 00:16:43,780
if you keep watching.

183
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:44,980
No money.

184
00:16:44,980 --> 00:16:46,450
You can watch me, too.

185
00:16:46,450 --> 00:16:47,610
You...

186
00:16:54,690 --> 00:16:56,220
What?

187
00:16:59,780 --> 00:17:01,570
I find that

188
00:17:02,250 --> 00:17:03,940
the more worried you are,

189
00:17:03,940 --> 00:17:05,610
the happier you look.

190
00:17:06,580 --> 00:17:09,330
Yet you talk in a serious way

191
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:12,540
when you feel relaxed.

192
00:17:20,460 --> 00:17:21,580
Is there

193
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:23,120
anything you want to ask me?

194
00:17:24,610 --> 00:17:27,250
Shen Tianshu said
you used Could-impelling Palm.

195
00:17:27,250 --> 00:17:28,760
What is that?

196
00:17:29,460 --> 00:17:31,370
You have top martial arts.

197
00:17:31,370 --> 00:17:33,850
How come you were bullied

198
00:17:33,850 --> 00:17:35,900
by a gang of rascals?

199
00:17:36,420 --> 00:17:37,730
Moreover,

200
00:17:37,730 --> 00:17:39,850
what is the Color of Ocean and Heaven
that you are after?

201
00:17:41,060 --> 00:17:42,460
Xie Yun.

202
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:44,420
Why do you have

203
00:17:44,420 --> 00:17:46,010
so many secrets?

204
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:51,420
Judging from your look,

205
00:17:51,420 --> 00:17:53,250
you must be thinking

206
00:17:53,250 --> 00:17:55,940
how to fool me with your lies.

207
00:17:55,940 --> 00:17:57,490
I won’t ask.

208
00:18:01,060 --> 00:18:02,010
No.

209
00:18:06,700 --> 00:18:07,850
OK.

210
00:18:07,850 --> 00:18:09,060
I’m leaving

211
00:18:09,060 --> 00:18:10,330
if you don’t.

212
00:18:17,330 --> 00:18:17,940
By the way.

213
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:24,580
Take this back.

214
00:18:37,010 --> 00:18:38,580
Things are done.

215
00:18:38,580 --> 00:18:40,210
You can take it back.

216
00:18:42,610 --> 00:18:44,300
When Miss Wu asks about it,

217
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:45,610
you can explain.

218
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:58,130
What is it?

219
00:19:16,210 --> 00:19:17,320
Xie Yun.

220
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:21,050
Are you pretending nothing happened?

221
00:19:24,730 --> 00:19:25,900
You...

222
00:19:26,820 --> 00:19:27,820
You...

223
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:31,970
Where will you stay?

224
00:19:33,130 --> 00:19:35,250
The guest room here.

225
00:19:36,460 --> 00:19:39,130
This place is indeed a wonderland.

226
00:19:39,130 --> 00:19:41,490
It’s cool and pleasing in summer.

227
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:42,720
I want to stay a while longer.

228
00:19:44,090 --> 00:19:45,300
Get yourself recovered.

229
00:19:45,300 --> 00:19:46,180
Then

230
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:48,490
take me to have a tour around.

231
00:19:49,330 --> 00:19:50,850
You know the scenes here

232
00:19:50,850 --> 00:19:52,540
better than me, don’t you?

233
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,250
You are acting.

234
00:20:00,490 --> 00:20:03,890
That’s not like what you would say.

235
00:20:04,970 --> 00:20:06,780
What should I say then?

236
00:20:06,780 --> 00:20:09,130
Should I say you may
put on some weight

237
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:10,490
and be my princess?

238
00:20:20,700 --> 00:20:22,180
Are you all right?

239
00:20:31,210 --> 00:20:32,730
Of course.

240
00:20:32,730 --> 00:20:34,090
I’m absolutely fine.

241
00:20:34,940 --> 00:20:37,210
Why are you after
the Color of Ocean and Heaven?

242
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:43,210
I don’t want it to fall into
the wrong hands.

243
00:20:47,730 --> 00:20:49,490
Since you’ve known it,

244
00:20:49,490 --> 00:20:51,610
I can tell you the truth.

245
00:20:55,210 --> 00:20:57,090
Chuchu’s Longevity Lock,

246
00:20:57,090 --> 00:20:58,530
the Mountain Sword’s scabbard.

247
00:20:59,370 --> 00:21:00,810
And your family’s gold bracelet.

248
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:02,730
These are

249
00:21:02,730 --> 00:21:04,690
important items to open
the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

250
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:09,370
Alright.

251
00:21:09,370 --> 00:21:10,460
Stop asking.

252
00:21:10,460 --> 00:21:12,580
You have so many questions.

253
00:21:14,490 --> 00:21:15,700
Xie Yun.

254
00:21:36,780 --> 00:21:37,900
I...

255
00:21:41,370 --> 00:21:43,970
I won’t be so impulsive again.

256
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:50,450
I’ll tell you wherever I go.

257
00:21:51,970 --> 00:21:53,660
I’ll talk to you first.

258
00:21:57,820 --> 00:21:58,850
How is it?

259
00:22:02,970 --> 00:22:04,180
Sure.

260
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:05,940
Anything else?

261
00:22:08,090 --> 00:22:09,200
And...

262
00:22:22,970 --> 00:22:24,460
No more.

263
00:22:24,970 --> 00:22:26,570
I thought you’d hold back for some days.

264
00:22:52,660 --> 00:22:54,660
I knew you couldn’t help asking me

265
00:22:54,660 --> 00:22:55,780
and caring about me.

266
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,730
But in this way,

267
00:23:01,730 --> 00:23:03,330
I’ll know, in your heart,

268
00:23:03,330 --> 00:23:05,300
I mean something to you.

269
00:23:12,780 --> 00:23:15,210
I’m just meddlesome, maybe.

270
00:23:21,610 --> 00:23:23,270
Why bother to come here?

271
00:24:04,470 --> 00:24:05,550
Chuchu.

272
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:06,870
Sheng.

273
00:24:14,820 --> 00:24:16,300
I... I come to see

274
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:18,730
if you get better.

275
00:24:18,730 --> 00:24:20,900
I... I’m much better.

276
00:24:23,580 --> 00:24:25,090
Sorry

277
00:24:25,090 --> 00:24:26,660
to let you worry.

278
00:24:33,530 --> 00:24:34,830
Now

279
00:24:35,460 --> 00:24:37,970
you are safe here.

280
00:24:38,610 --> 00:24:40,030
Your brother

281
00:24:41,300 --> 00:24:43,010
is out alone.

282
00:24:43,010 --> 00:24:44,540
It’s worrisome.

283
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:46,420
Why don’t you get him here

284
00:24:46,420 --> 00:24:48,180
to be with you?

285
00:24:48,180 --> 00:24:49,730
You can take care of each other.

286
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:57,900
It’s fine if you don’t agree.

287
00:24:57,900 --> 00:24:58,930
I agree.

288
00:25:05,970 --> 00:25:07,820
Are you back alive shamelessly?

289
00:25:07,820 --> 00:25:09,820
He’s my man.

